 + 2% MDEF + 300 Spell burst activation rate + 3% Magic evasion - 5%<br /></span></span><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong style="font-family: &quot;font-size:medium;"><u>▲Sauro III&nbsp;<span style="color: #4ae619;">(✓)</span>:</u></strong><span style="font-family: &quot;font-size:medium;">&nbsp;Melee +3% to all elements, All magics +3%, Delay -0.5 sec, Autoskill +3%, ATK/MATK+30, Neutral resistance+5%</span></span><br style="font-family: &quot;font-size:medium;" /><span style="font-family: 'times new roman';"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-weight: bold; color: #2264f0;"><u>Not out yet:</u></span><br /><strong><u>▲Selee zauga II <span style="color: #4ae619;">(✓)</span>:</u></strong> MATK +5% Spell burst +3% MaxMP +3% Melee R -25%<br /><strong><u>▲Sophis:</u></strong> INT + 16<br /><strong><u>▲Dunkelis:</u></strong> Magic + 3% spell burst rate + 5% Magic penetration + 20% MaxMP - 50%<br /><strong><u>▲Fiona:</u></strong> MATK + 4% Magic penetration + 5% MaxMP + 7%<br /><strong><u>▲Vida:</u></strong> ATK + 8% MATK + 8% Auto skill activation - 5% Physical and magic resistance - 20%<br /></span><span style="font-size: medium; font-weight: bold; color: #ff0000;"><u><span style="font-size: large;"><br />AL crystas SK-focused:</span></u><span style="font-size: large;"><br /></span></span><span style="font-size: medium;"><u style="font-weight: bold;">▲MP Cost-6%<span style="color: #ff7000;">(⭘)</span><br />▲INT+1, 2, 3, DEX+1, 2, 3, etc<span style="color: #ff7000;">(⭘)</span><br />▲Gatekeeper <span style="color: #4ae619;">(✓)</span>:</u> If a stat has more than 350 points into it, slight boost to this stat:<br /> INT&gt;350=MATK +2% MaxMP +5% INT +3 <br />DEX&gt;350=Item Delay -0.2s Skill Delay -0.2s Melee Pierce +2% Magic Pierce +2% DEX +3 <br />CRT&gt;350=Critical damage +3% Absolute Evasion +2% Magic Evasion +2% CRT +3<br /><u style="font-weight: bold;">▲Zazel<span style="color: #ff7000;">(⭘)</span>:</u></span><span style="font-size: medium;"> ATK+15, ATK+2%, MATK+20, MATK+2%</span><strong style="font-size: medium;"><u><br />▲Cheltil:</u></strong><span style="font-size: medium;"> Skill delay -1 second, Item delay +0.5 second</span><u style="font-size: medium; font-weight: bold;"><br /></u></span><span style="font-family: 'times new roman';"><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong><u>▲Mamonea:</u></strong>Critical damage +5%, Critical rate +10%, Magic R -10%</span><br /><u style="font-size: medium;"><strong>▲Ouvel <span style="color: #4ae619;">(✓)</span>:</strong></u><span style="font-size: medium;"> MATK &amp; ATK+6%, MaxHP &amp; MaxMP-10%</span><strong style="font-size: medium;"><u><br />▲Enina:</u></strong><span style="font-size: medium;"> Small ATK up by Lv, MATK up by Lv, Absolute evasion -10%, Magic evasion -10%</span><u style="font-size: medium;"><strong><br />▲Sauro II <span style="color: #4ae619;">(✓)</span>:</strong></u><span style="font-size: medium;">Melee +3% to all elements, All magic +3%, Delay -0.5 sec, Autoskill +2%</span><strong style="font-size: medium;"><u><br />▲Cordal:</u></strong><span style="font-size: medium;">&nbsp;Autoskills +3% Critical damage +3%</span><strong style="font-size: medium;"><u><br />▲Arick:&nbsp;</u></strong><span style="font-size: medium;">Critical Damage +6% Melee and Magic R -5% Magic evasion -12%<br /></span></span><strong style="font-family: &quot;font-size:medium;"><u><span style="font-size: medium;">▲Bernhardt:</span></u></strong><span style="font-family: &quot;font-size:medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">&nbsp;Stun time -1 second, Critical damage +4%, Magic evasion +5%<br /></span></span><u style="font-family: &quot;font-size:medium;"><strong>▲Sauro III&nbsp;<span style="color: #4ae619;">(✓)</span>:</strong></u><span style="font-family: &quot;font-size:medium;">&nbsp;Melee +3% to all elements, All magics +3%, Delay -0.5 sec, Autoskill +3%, ATK/MATK+30, Neutral resistance+5%</span><span style="font-family: &quot;font-size:medium;"><br /></span><span style="font-family: 'times new roman';"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-weight: bold; color: #2264f0;">Not out yet:<br /></span><strong><u>▲Cordal II:</u></strong> Autoskills +5% Critical damage +5%<br /><u><strong>▲Vasaria </strong><span style="font-weight: bold; color: #4ae619;">(✓)</span><strong>:</strong></u>&nbsp;Water tolerance + 20% absolute hit + 20% Critical damage + 8%<br /><strong><u>▲Tarna:</u></strong>&nbsp;Critical Damage + 4% Counterattack Rate + 5% Magic Resistance - 15%<br /><strong><u>▲Vida <span style="color: #4ae619;">(✓)</span>:</u></strong> ATK + 8% MATK + 8% Auto skill activation - 5% Physical and magic resistance - 20%<br /></span></span></div>
